    <section id="id44956405">
      <title>RELATIONSHIPS</title>
      <para id="id44956528">Next, YOU will be looking at RELATIONSHIPS</para>
      <para id="id44956533">The way that people deal with each other is complicated. YOU know that.</para>
      <para id="id44956537">You either experience it yourself or see how others sometimes struggle.</para>
      <para id="id44956542">The relationship between a child and the parent is sometimes fine but often tense.</para>
      <para id="id44956547">Feelings come into play. How sensitive one is affects the relationship.</para>
      <para id="id44956552">Feeling good about yourself certainly helps.</para>
      <para id="id44956555">And knowing HOW to deal with certain problems also helps.</para>
